I did get it building with CMake after making some adjustments.  I remember finding some changes on github that allowed CMake to find the FreeBSD package for protobufs.  I deleted those changes though and need to find them again.  When I do, I'll keep better track of it and put together a patch.

My issue was after building the libraries, I didn't know how to get the Ruby gem to be built against them.
